      <title>世界银行称未来两年巴基斯坦经济增速预计低于 3%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/pakistan-growth-seen-below-3-for-next-2-years-world-bank-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据世界银行的最新预测，巴基斯坦本财年经济增长预计将有所回升，但未来两年仍将保持在3%以下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/pakistan-growth-seen-below-3-for-next-2-years-world-bank-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 07:40:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>无人机袭击远离乌克兰边境的俄罗斯鞑靼斯坦地区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/drones-strike-russia-s-tatarstan-region-far-from-ukraine-border</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二早些时候，无人机袭击了俄罗斯鞑靼斯坦地区，这是俄罗斯入侵乌克兰以来的首次，击中了距离乌克兰边境近1500公里（约930英里）的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/drones-strike-russia-s-tatarstan-region-far-from-ukraine-border</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 07:26:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗誓言对以色列袭击驻叙利亚领事馆进行报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/iran-says-sent-us-message-over-deadly-israeli-strike-on-compound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗表示将对以色列对其驻叙利亚大使馆大院发动致命空袭进行报复——这是双方因加沙战争而不断升级的代理人冲突中罕见的直接对抗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/iran-says-sent-us-message-over-deadly-israeli-strike-on-compound</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 06:11:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>调查显示中国取代美国成为东南亚最受青睐的合作伙伴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/china-topples-us-as-se-asia-s-favored-partner-survey-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新的调查显示，随着华盛顿在从地区经济参与到以色列-哈马斯战争等一系列关键问题上节节败退，中国已经取代美国成为东南亚国家的首要结盟选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/china-topples-us-as-se-asia-s-favored-partner-survey-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 04:56:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国将扩大预算缺口 42 亿美元以刺激经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/thailand-to-widen-2025-budget-gap-by-4-2-billion-to-spur-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国内阁已批准一项计划，将明年的预算赤字目标扩大约42亿美元，以帮助刺激东南亚第二大经济体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/thailand-to-widen-2025-budget-gap-by-4-2-billion-to-spur-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 04:51:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油巨头在保加利亚转向俄罗斯的战略中占据中心舞台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-02/as-bulgaria-unpicks-russian-ties-oil-giant-lukoil-looks-to-sell-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[通过驱逐卢克石油公司来解除与俄罗斯的关键业务联系将标志着一个时代的结束。但并不是每个人都高兴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-02/as-bulgaria-unpicks-russian-ties-oil-giant-lukoil-looks-to-sell-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 04:00:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡洗钱案创纪录者被判入狱 13 个月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/singapore-sees-first-guilty-plea-in-2-2-billion-laundering-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡创纪录的 30 亿新元（22 亿美元）洗钱案中第一个认罪的人被判处 13 个月监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/singapore-sees-first-guilty-plea-in-2-2-billion-laundering-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 01:55:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>秘鲁总统博卢阿特在关键投票前因劳力士丑闻而改组内阁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/peru-s-boluarte-reshuffles-cabinet-amid-rolex-scandal-ahead-of-key-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[秘鲁总统迪娜·博卢阿特 (Dina Boluarte) 改组了内阁，试图应对因使用奢侈手表而引发的危机，而她的政府即将在国会进行关键投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/peru-s-boluarte-reshuffles-cabinet-amid-rolex-scandal-ahead-of-key-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 01:29:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>主厨何塞·安德烈斯称援助人员在加沙罢工中丧生</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/aid-workers-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-gaza-jose-andres-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[名厨何塞·安德烈斯 (José Andrés) 创立的救灾组织在 X 上发帖称，世界中央厨房 (World Central Kitchen) 的 7 名救援人员在以色列军队对加沙的空袭中丧生。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/aid-workers-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-gaza-jose-andres-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 00:26:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜在韩国投票前发射弹道导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/north-korea-fires-ballistic-missile-ahead-of-south-s-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在韩国议会席位全国选举前几天，朝鲜发射了至少一枚疑似中程弹道导弹，以展示武力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/north-korea-fires-ballistic-missile-ahead-of-south-s-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 23:07:24 GMT</pubDate>
